snippet.title: Diana and New Children's Magazine Love, Diana! | How to keep kids busy at home
snippet.description:
Parents, you can find Love, Diana at Tesco!
Love, Diana Princess of Play Dolls: http://bit.ly/3rbZIH7
Love, Diana Mash Ups Dolls: http://bit.ly/3tHzyO3

Diana wants to play. Dad knows exactly how to keep the child busy. He introduces Diana to the new children's magazine "Love, Diana", which captivates the girl for a long time! Diana and Dad are having fun together!
Thanks for watching!
